  "prompt": "What is gold digger?",
  "response": "The term \"gold digger\" typically refers to someone who forms relationships with others primarily to extract money, gifts, or other material benefits from them. This term is often used in a derogatory manner to describe individuals who are perceived to be exploiting their partners for financial gain rather than genuine affection or love. The concept can apply to both men and women, though historically it has been more commonly associated with women.",
